      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Full service history. No defects.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-standard specimen that satisfies even the most discerning collector's eye. This vehicle has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one, and it shows. The exterior paint retains a mirror-like depth with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings; it has been treated with a multi-layer ceramic coating to ensure its luster remains permanent. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium upholstery remains taut with no bolster wear, the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty liners since new, and the interior still carries a faint 'new car' aroma. Every button, switch, and digital display operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, documented service history performed exclusively by master technicians at authorized dealerships. It has never seen salt or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the hood. This isn't just a used car; it is a pristine example of automotive excellence, offered with all original keys, manuals, and a thick folder of maintenance records. If you are looking for a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor, your search ends here.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
