    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I have babyed this car since day one, and it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in absolute pristine condition\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. It drives like a total dream and still has that wonderful new-car feel. I'm looking for a great new home for it, so feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look. You won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
